tool_description: URL/ HTML content will convert to PDF file of the desired size.
name: URL HTML to PDF
title: URL HTML to PDF

api_list.name: URL To PDF
api_list.description:
Converts given URL into PDF 

Width and Height are in Pixels.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://url-html-to-pdf.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/pdf/url-to-pdf"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "url-html-to-pdf.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
